<!-- end header --><div id="leftcontent">
	
	<div class="post">
		 <h1 id="post-2"><a name="content">About Us</a></h1>
		
		<div class="storycontent">
			<h4 style="text-align: center;"></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><img class="size-medium wp-image-790" src="http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/DTM-logo2-300x100.jpg" alt="DTM logo" width="300" height="100" srcset="http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/DTM-logo2-300x100.jpg 300w, http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/DTM-logo2.jpg 705w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Situated atop a small hill overlooking Quance Park in Delhi, Ontario, this open-concept museum, built in 1979 as a model of typical tobacco pack barn, houses a large agricultural collection which includes exhibits on tobacco, ginseng and alternate crops grown in Norfolk County.  Permanent and featured exhibits highlight local community history and its diverse multicultural heritage.  Throughout the year, the Museum hosts fundraising and community development events for people of all ages.  Canada’s only tobacco museum is open year-round and is available for rental for small functions and to community groups with seating for 60.</h4>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_3195.jpg" rel="lightbox[2]" title="About Us"><img class="size-medium wp-image-791 alignleft" src="http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_3195-300x225.jpg" alt="IMG_3195" width="300" height="225" srcset="http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_3195-300x225.jpg 300w, http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_3195-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a>  <a href="http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_4141.jpg" rel="lightbox[2]" title="About Us"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-792" src="http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_4141-300x225.jpg" alt="IMG_4141" width="300" height="225" srcset="http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_4141-300x225.jpg 300w, http://delhimuseum.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/IMG_4141-1024x768.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></p>
<h1 style="text-align: center;"></h1>
<p><!-- PHP 5.x --></p>
